# Team Speak 3 Configuration

![TSConfig](https://i.imgur.com/48oxvBg.png)

To set up push to talk in Team speak 3 go to tools, options

![Push Talk](https://i.imgur.com/DRERsNv.png)

select capture. Set Push to talk under activation and choose the push to talk key. Select the chosen push to talk key.

## How to copy Teamspeak Identity

![Identities](https://i.imgur.com/dXgHOe2.png)

Under tools click identities,

![Unique ID](https://i.imgur.com/Ry8IOdY.png)

and copy the unique id.

![forums](https://i.imgur.com/4CWQOLr.png)

Go to the [forums](https://www.clanaod.net/forums/cmps_index.php) and in the upper right click settings

![Member Info](https://i.imgur.com/VTRy1W0.png)

In the left column choose Edit AOD Member Info

![Identity](https://i.imgur.com/wjwC9z7.png)

Paste the teamspeak identity verify other information is correct and click save changes.

## How to Set a Bookmark

![Add bookmark](https://i.imgur.com/jscPgM2.png)

Click bookmarks add to bookmarks.

![Set Nickname](https://i.imgur.com/p7Pl7Dl.png)

Verify address is correct. Set Nickname. This is also where the default channel will be set later. Connect via the bookmark and verify the name is correct.
